Package: RobustTRegression
Type: Package
Title: Estimation of Degrees of Freedom and Regression Parameters using Robust t-Regression methods
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Amanda", "Ng", email = "waiyuamanda.ng@mail.utoronto.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides several methods for estimating the degrees of freedom parameter (nu)
    and regression coefficients (beta) in robust t-regression models, including profile likelihood,
    adjusted profile likelihood, Jeffreys prior, and marginalized approaches.
